  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47a621783cb453147b01764dde5ed130, type: 3}
  m_Name: WilliamIntro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - So... the Moonwarden line still endures.
  - I am William, guardian of this forest and keeper of the Heartgrove.
  - For many years, I waited for someone to return.
  - The heart of the magical world grows weaker with each passing moon.
  - The balance cannot sustain itself much longer.
  - There is only one way to restore it.
  - A restoration draught once crafted by the Moonwardens themselves.
  - A potion woven from several ancient remedies working in harmony.
  - Selene knew its recipe...
  - If her spirit remains within the cottage, then she can teach you.
  - Learn the old brews. Restore the meadow.
  - Strengthen the magic flowing through these lands...
  - Only then will the Heartgrove awaken again.
